description: 37 years ago today a-ha’s Take On Me was the big song, Britney Spears is back at it again on Twitter, Kanye West is being sued by George Floyd’s family, Taylor Swift's new album is coming out, security architects are a thing, we need a YouTube handle, Jayn is showing off a new trend, it’s National New Friends Day, a poll on the top traits we look for in friends, people are skipping Thanksgiving to save money, should all cars have a feature that prevents you from speeding, and Vinnie reads your texts!
